original_title: Rails to Suburbia: The Strang Line & Overland Park
overview: Good transportation has always been essential to the idea of a suburban retreat. In 1906, I was Strang's interurban railway; today, it's the automobile. Through archival photos, interviews with historians and public officials, and narration fran television star Michael Gross, Rails to Suburbia traces the evolution of a premier American community.
title: Rails to Suburbia: The Strang Line & Overland Park
